<item>
            <title>[HBASE-2817] Allow separate HBASE_REGIONSERVER_HEAPSIZE and HBASE_MASTER_HEAPSIZE</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2817</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Right now we have a single HBASE_HEAPSIZE configuration. This isn&apos;t that great, since the HMaster doesn&apos;t really need much ram compared to the region servers. We should allow different java options and heapsize for the different daemon types.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Probably worth breaking out THRIFT, REST, AVRO, etc, as well.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
